geneVariantDescriptions.description: IL6 positive indicates the presence of the IL6 gene, mRNA, and/or protein.

evidence.efficacyEvidence: In a preclinical study, Gemzar (gemcitabine) and Platinol (cisplatin) inhibited tumor growth in non-small cell lung cancer cells harboring EGFR E746-A750del and with intact autocrine IL6 signaling in xenongraft models (PMID: 26744529).
